/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Duran-Duran-playing-live-in-London.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Duran-Duran-playing-live-in-London-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Duran-Duran-playing-live-in-London-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Duran-Duran-playing-live-in-London-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Duran-Duran-playing-live-in-London-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Duran-Duran-playing-live-in-London-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran)</a>表示，他们“很乐意”与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rogers">尼罗·罗杰斯 (Nile Rogers</a> ) 和马克·朗森 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-ronson">Mark Ronson)</a>作为特邀嘉宾一起参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/glastonbury">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-headliners-2024-rumours-bookies-3458989">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年头条新闻：明年谁将登上金字塔顶？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位 80 年代的流行偶像以前从未在 Worthy Farm 演出过，但表示如果有合适的位置，他们很愿意出现。他们之前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/duran-duran-interview-2023-simon-le-bon-john-taylor-glastonbury-wet-leg-3432534">与<em>《NME》</em>谈论过他们希望有一天能参加这个音乐节。</a></p><p>主唱西蒙·勒邦 (Simon Le Bon) 在 BBC 的<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0gqkzx7" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Headliners</em></a>播客中说道：“我想参加格拉斯顿伯里音乐节。我不想成为一名投注者，但我希望杜兰·杜兰获得正确的位置。无论如何，这是我们不应该在广播中进行的对话。我很乐意这样做。老实说，我想要一个夜间时段，而且必须在金字塔舞台上。”</p><p>当被问及是否会邀请特别嘉宾参加演出时，贝斯手约翰·泰勒表示，他们希望看到乐队以前的一些合作者与他们一起登上舞台，包括罗杰斯和罗森，他们过去都曾为乐队制作过作品。泰勒说：“你必须把尼罗河带出来，也许还有马克。”</p><p>回忆起第一次见到罗杰斯时，泰勒继续说道：“82 年，我们和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondie">Blondie</a>在新泽西州的后台，Nile 说‘我听到了你的声音！’” Duran 成立时，其主要影响之一是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chic">Chic</a> 。当时没有多少人这么说。人们正在焚烧迪斯科唱片。</p><p> “当时一支年轻的英国乐队放弃了 Chic 的影响力，这对他来说非常重要，因为没有人这样做。了解尼罗河就等于爱他。你想和他成为朋友，他在各个层面上都是一个非常慷慨的人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3536453" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3536453" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3536453" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live.jpg" alt="尼罗·罗杰斯" width="2000" height="1271" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Nile-Rogers-playing-live-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3536453" class="wp-caption-text">尼罗·罗杰斯——图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>上周（11 月 5 日），格拉斯顿伯里音乐节组织者艾米丽·伊维斯 (Emily Eavis) 回应<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-madonna-reportedly-set-to-headline-festival-3530560">了有关音乐节头条新闻的最新消息，称这些消息“不真实”。</a></p><p>有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜</a>将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>和酷玩乐队 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay)</a>一起成为明年音乐节的主角。</p><p>伊维斯平息了谣言，他说：“一如既往，人们对谁在格拉斯顿伯里演奏有很多猜测和兴奋。目前我们正在夜以继日地制作阵容，但每天仍然在变化。关于我们已确认的头条新闻的故事是不真实的。 As always, we love your enthusiasm and guesswork – but accurate news on headliners will be with you sometime in the new year!”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-postpones-2024-ticket-sales-3529071">Glastonbury also announced it was postponing the scheduled ticket sales for the 2024 festival</a> due to issues with some registrations.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-announces-2024-ticket-sale-details-3506575">As announced back in September</a> , coach and ticket packages had been due to go on sale at 6pm GMT on November 2 ahead of a general sale at 9am GMT on November 5.</p><p> However, organisers confirmed on social media that both sales have been delayed by two weeks. Coach and ticket packages will now be available at 6pm GMT on Thursday, November 16, with the general sale following at 9am GMT on Sunday, November 19.</p><p> Next year&#39;s festival will take place at Worthy Farm between 26-30 June.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-duran-duran-say-theyd-love-to-play-pyramid-stage-with-nile-rogers-and-mark-ronson-3536452">Glastonbury 2024: Duran Duran say they&#39;d “love” to play Pyramid Stage with Nile Rogers and Mark Ronson</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
